<ul>
  <li>what can help save fuel and reduce pollution ?</li>
  <li>Contributing to a constant flow of traffic by thinking ahead and driving correspondingly</li>
  <li>Paying attention to the fuel consumption of a motor vehicle when buying it</li>
  <li>Using public transport, a bicycle or walking, wherever possible</li>
