<p>When overtaking, what do you have to observe regarding spacing?
Ihre L√∂sung
Maintain an adequate space to the side, particularly between the vehicle and persons (right)
To maintain a greater side spacing towards multi-lane vehicles than towards single-lane vehicles
To maintain an adequate space to the side between the vehicle and other road users (right)</p>

<p>A strong side wind is blowing from the right. When are you particularly exposed to danger when overtaking?
Ihre L√∂sung
When you enter the slipstream of the truck (right)
When you leave the slipstream of the truck (right)
When you change lane after overtaking</p>

